# ==============================================================================
# ADVENT AUTOMATION 2025 - API KEYS CONFIGURATION
# ==============================================================================
#
# IMPORTANT: Each day project REQUIRES its own API keys for security and usage tracking
#
# NAMING CONVENTION:
# - Day-specific keys (REQUIRED): KEY_OPENAI_DAY01, KEY_ANTHROPIC_DAY01, etc.
# - Default keys (DEV ONLY): KEY_OPENAI, KEY_ANTHROPIC
#
# ==============================================================================

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# FOR DEVELOPERS (Testing/Development Only)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Use these keys for general development and testing
# DO NOT share these keys with clients
# Clients should use day-specific keys below

KEY_OPENAI=your_dev_openai_key_here
KEY_ANTHROPIC=your_dev_anthropic_key_here

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# FOR CLIENTS (Production/Deployment - REQUIRED)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Each day project needs its own keys for:
# - Independent usage tracking
# - Security isolation
# - Cost control per project

# Day 01 Project Keys (REQUIRED for day01/)
KEY_OPENAI_DAY01=your_client_openai_key_for_day01
KEY_ANTHROPIC_DAY01=your_client_anthropic_key_for_day01

# Day 02 Project Keys (REQUIRED for day02/)
# KEY_OPENAI_DAY02=your_client_openai_key_for_day02
# KEY_ANTHROPIC_DAY02=your_client_anthropic_key_for_day02

# Day 03 Project Keys (REQUIRED for day03/)
# KEY_OPENAI_DAY03=your_client_openai_key_for_day03
# KEY_ANTHROPIC_DAY03=your_client_anthropic_key_for_day03

# ... Continue for all days (04-25) as needed

# ==============================================================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS FOR CLIENTS:
# ==============================================================================
#
# 1. Copy this file: cp config/.env.example config/.env
#
# 2. For each day project you're using:
#    - Get your OpenAI API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
#    - Get your Anthropic API key from: https://console.anthropic.com/
#    - Add them to the corresponding KEY_*_DAY## variables
#
# 3. Example for Day 01:
#    KEY_OPENAI_DAY01=sk-proj-abc123...
#    KEY_ANTHROPIC_DAY01=sk-ant-xyz789...
#
# 4. DO NOT use or configure the KEY_OPENAI and KEY_ANTHROPIC defaults
#    Those are only for the developer's testing environment
#
# 5. Each project day is independent - you only need keys for the days you use
#
# ==============================================================================
# SECURITY NOTES:
# ==============================================================================
# - Never commit .env to version control (already in .gitignore)
# - Each day uses isolated keys for better security and tracking
# - You can create separate API keys per day for granular usage monitoring
# ==============================================================================
